rs while gaining revenue, as thugs in danger areas are spying on you in the dark.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445310/extras/e228ae0d2fb4fed3ae1f107a4be7637c.avif?t=1730332914\" width=616 height=200 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Great Land</h2>It's a customizable continent system for hardcore players, where you can create a continent of your own, grow crops and dig new resources on it. Everything is yours, but it's pricey to maintain it. So call your guild to protect the land together!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445310/extras/0da2191a6809bd6eedccf1f1004ff983.poster.avif?t=1730332914\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445310/extras/0da2191a6809bd6eedccf1f1004ff983.webm?t=1730332914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445310/extras/0da2191a6809bd6eedccf1f1004ff983.mp4?t=1730332914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
